From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Loop User <user@example.com>
Date: Mon, 16 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add TDD toggle to Apple Watch IOB row

This patch adds the ability to toggle between Active Insulin (IOB) and
Total Daily Dose (TDD) by tapping the IOB row on the Apple Watch.

Changes:
- Add TDD property to WatchContext
- Add computed property for TDD display
- Fetch TDD data in WatchDataManager
- Add tap gesture handling in ChartHUDController
- Add TDD display method in HUDRowController
- Add TDD localization strings

The toggle is non-persistent and resets to IOB on each app launch.

